reviewText: practical is the best dvd series for introductory small circle jujitsu techniques. a great addition to your growing home self defense collection.

This is an awsome video for anyone who is intrested in self protection. Even if you have little or no exsperience, it helps. If you are any type of martial artist, you will greatly benefit from this video. It will take what you already know and just make it more efficient.

Sensei Ed Melaugh makes it look so easy, he shows you how to make the attacker make mistakes and just hand you their limbs so they can be locked out quickly with out using strength.  it is a must have dvd.
